text: New York State Route 9G (NY 9G) is a road in Dutchess County, New York, United States. It starts at US 9 in Poughkeepsie and follows the Hudson River as it goes north. It crosses Route 9 just north of Rhinebeck and ends in Hudson. ==References== ==Other websites== *Route log Category:Roads in New York (state)
title: New York State Route 9G
